{"word":"G3471 - μωραίνω - mōraínō - mo-rah'-ee-no - Become fool","slug":"G3471","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μωραίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mōraínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mo-rah'-ee-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Become fool"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03C9;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - mo&#x0304;raino&#x0304;</b> - <i>mo-rah'ee-no</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3474\">G3474</a>; to <i>become insipid</i>; figuratively to <i>make</i> (passively <i>act</i>) as a <i>simpleton:</i> - become fool, make foolish, lose savour."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3472\">G3472</a>, <a href=\"#/G3473\">G3473</a>, <a href=\"#/G3474\">G3474</a>"}]}